Hello,

JUnit seems to be a really great thing.
What pleases me the best is that the core functionality
is very very uncoupled from the extensions,
in the very simple package junit.framework.

Only a few classes, with no dependancies (except on java.lang),
that's a great design.

But, there are 2 items that seem unrelated to the core functionality:

- class TestFailure
- interface Protectable

They aren't really documented.
Where can I find real documentation about those items?

Regards,

Luc
